tags.description:
Pieces of official MLP content, without edits and only reasonable animation loops, are **always** safe.  
**Cannot be combined with any other rating.**
tags.name: safe

tags.description:
A four legged animal and main race of the show. Not to be tagged on characters drawn as Anthro or Semi-anthro.  
May be tagged on images with "Bipedal" tag.  
Example:  
>>1426211s >>1617278s
tags.name: pony

tags.description: This tag is to be used when there is only one character shown in the image. Note that disembodied or offscreen body parts make an image no longer solo; use [solo focus](/tags/solo+focus) for such cases.
tags.name: solo

tags.description:
Tag for any character that has not appeared in official media or merchandise; that is, a fan-made character, regardless of how popular they may be.  
**Note:** [Ponified](/tags/ponified) people/characters from other media are ***not*** OCs.
tags.name: oc

tags.description: There are no characters from the show, comics, toys or other official media in the image.
tags.name: oc only

tags.description: Do not use this tag when the clothes in question are being worn by a character as they normally appear, such as Granny Smith's kerchief or Mayor Mare's collar, unless other articles of clothing are present.
tags.name: clothes

tags.description:
Related background tags: [transparent background](/tags/transparent+background), [abstract background](/tags/abstract+background), [gradient background](/tags/gradient+background). A fully transparent background is always considered a simple background, but a gradient or abstract background is never a simple background. 

>>285886s
tags.name: simple background
tags.short_description: A flat background of one solid color or complete transparency.
